content.html: CS Customer Health

Customer Health Framework
  • Phase 5: Customer Health Summary
  • Product Value
    • Usage/Growth
      • MVP DONE: % new enrollments <> per quarter [Data Source:  View - USAGE_LEARNERS_BY_MONTH_AGGREGATE]
      • MVP DONE: NPS counts by type (promoter / passive / detractor) [Data Source: View - USAGE_NET_PROMOTER_SCORE]
      • MVP DONE: Avg Course Rating [Data Source: View - USAGE_PRODUCT_REVIEWS]
    • Business Value
      • Product Alignment
        • Phase 2: Content Type [PENDING DATA/PROSERV rec to CS: Provide parameters to classify each course into Product Strategy Framework > Content Type]
        • Phase 2: Instructional Method [PENDING DATA/PROSERV rec to CS: Provide parameters to classify each course into Product Strategy Framework > Instructional Method]
        • Distribution Method [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
  • Phase 3/4: Relationship -->
    • CSM Sentiment [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
    • Customer NPS ("Does the customer recommend our product?") [PENDING CS; Data Source: Email survey tool]
    • Loyalty [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
      • # of Renewals Completed
      • # of Referrals (of BenchPrep to others) []
  • Phase 3/4: Financials -->
    • Risk Evaluation [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
      • Assessment level
      • Accounts receivable
      • Customer's Financial health
    • Annual ARR
    • Potential for Growth [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
      • Accounts Receivable
      • # of Days outstanding [PENDING CS / Accounting; Data Source: ???]
    • Annual ARR [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]
    • Growth Potential [PENDING CS; Data Source: Salesforce]

widgets.title: Course Reviews / Ratings by Quarter
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to review score, presented as an average, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze learner satisfaction with the platform.

NPS Scores by Quarter
widgets.desc: The dynamic chart represents data pertaining to NPS (net promoter score - industry standard), presented in aggregate, and scoped to the level of permission for your account. Interact with and utilize this dashboard to analyze learners who answer the question "How likely are you to recommend your course to a friend".
